      <ReportItem port="443" svc_name="https" protocol="tcp" severity="3" pluginID="20007" pluginName="SSL Version 2 and 3 Protocol Detection" pluginFamily="General">
        <synopsis>The remote service encrypts traffic using a protocol with known weaknesses.</synopsis>
        <description>The remote service accepts connections using SSLv3. An attacker can exploit this to conduct man-in-the-middle attacks (POODLE).</description>
